{"name":"Batteries.Lean.Delaborator","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Lean.PrettyPrinter"],"declarations":[{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/batteries/blob/551ff2d7dffd7af914cdbd01abbd449fe3e3d428/Batteries/Lean/Delaborator.lean#L14-L25","name":"Lean.ppConst","line":14,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Batteries/Lean/Delaborator.html#Lean.ppConst","doc":"Pretty print a const expression using `delabConst` and generate terminfo.\nThis function avoids inserting `@` if the constant is for a function whose first\nargument is implicit, which is what the default `toMessageData` for `Expr` does.\nPanics if `e` is not a constant. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Batteries/Lean/Delaborator.html#Lean.ppConst\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">ppConst</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(e : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Lean.Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">Lean.MessageData</a></div></div>"}]}